"auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Sex-Pistols">Sex Pistols</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Guns-N-Roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a> 、 <a href="/artsits/Biffy-Clyro">Biffy Clyro</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Avenged-Sevenfold">Avenged Sevenfold</a>等乐队已宣布成为今年《Rock for People》的表演者。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/kneecap-film-review-biopic-michael-fassbender-3779661">《膝盖》评论：大胆、勇敢，是有史以来最好的音乐传记片之一</a></strong></li></ul><p>Rock For People 2025 计划于明年 6 月 11 日至 14 日在捷克赫拉德茨克拉洛韦的 Park 360 举行。新宣布的表演者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-slipknot-fontaines-d-c-idles-lead-rock-for-people-2025-line-up-3812937">包括之前透露的 Linkin Park 和 Slipknot</a>以及<a href="/artists/Fontaines-D-C">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="/artsits/IDLES">IDLES</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Poppy">Poppy</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、Skillet、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/in-flames">In Flames</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motionless-in-white">Motionless In White</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deafheaven">Deafheaven</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/house-of-protection">House of Protection</a>等乐队。</p><p>为了庆祝音乐节成立 30 周年，Guns N&#39; Roses 计划在周日（6 月 15 日）额外增加一天的活动来结束周末。法案中宣布的其他新名字包括<a href="/artists/Refused">Refused</a> 、Lorna Shore、 <a href="/artists/Sigrid">Sigrid、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marc-rebillet">Marc Rebillet</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ghost-inside">The Ghost Inside</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Circa-Waves">Circa Waves</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles-of-death-metal">Eagles of Death Metal</a> 。</p><p>门票现已发售，价格从 302 欧元到 782 欧元不等。提供全周末和单日通行证。您可以<a href="https://rockforpeople.cz/en/tickets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买门票。查看下面的完整阵容和每日分组。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD9klFiMCtA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;